          After creating your account, pick the learning path that fits your family best.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        {learningPaths.map((path) => (
          <div class={`relative bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 text-center ${!path.available ? 'opacity-70' : ''}`}>
            {path.available ? (
              <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-4 py-1 bg-mf-teal text-white text-xs font-display rounded-full">
                {path.subtitle}
              </div>
            ) : (
              <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-4 py-1 bg-gray-400 text-white text-xs font-display rounded-full">
                {path.subtitle}
              </div>
            )}
