          <p class="text-text-body font-corp-body text-sm">Absolutely. We are fully COPPA compliant and collect minimal data from children. Parents have full control. See our <a href="/privacy" class="text-mf-teal hover:text-mf-pink">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
        </div>
